# Bright Data configuration
# For a working proxy, set BRIGHTDATA_PROXY_URL directly to the full proxy URL from your Bright Data dashboard.
# Example:
# BRIGHTDATA_PROXY_URL=http://brd-customer-<your-customer-id>-zone-unblocker:<your-zone-password>@zproxy.lum-superproxy.io:22225
